description: This is the lowest priced 2 bed condo in South Boston! Perfect for first time home buyers, couples who are tired of paying rent, or a seasoned investor. 9 Gates St Unit 1 offers 2 bedrooms, 1 bathroom and a spacious PRIVATE patio. The condo's great layout allows for an open concept kitchen and living room with beautiful exposed brick! The roomy main bedroom also offers a walk in closet. The location of this condo is outstanding as you can walk to the local, vibrant restaurants and the Andrew Square Station is less than a mile away. Off of the private patio, the owner of this condo also has exclusive access to the shed, which allows for ample storage. Tough to find condos in South Boston under 600k, do not miss out on this opportunity!
